{[#]} {[%tqu "En","The most critcal line in the position. White to move.","","","d1c2","This is the most interesting move, in my opinion. Our idea is to stop Nc3.",10,"b3c4","was played in all the three games that have reached this position, but after",0]} 11. Qc2 $5 $146 {This is the most interesting move, in my opinion. Our idea is to stop Nc3.} (11. bxc4 {was played in all the three games that have reached this position, but after} Nc3 12. Qe1 Bxg2 13. Kxg2 $11 {Black is at least fine after both 13...Na4 or 13...bxc4.}) 11... cxb3 12. Nxb3 $44 {Just typical good compensation for White. Black's best is 12...Nd7, where after 13.Nc6, it's clear that White has all the fun.} *

